463
00:41:57.139 --> 00:41:57.973
Mama.

464
00:42:03.395 --> 00:42:04.855
Sudah berbulan-bulan sejak aku melihatmu.

465
00:42:06.815 --> 00:42:07.983
Anda tahu itu?

466
00:42:11.487 --> 00:42:12.947
Aku tahu.

467
00:42:13.531 --> 00:42:14.949
Tapi…

468
00:42:15.032 --> 00:42:17.034
